  "description": "Phat unison bass with 4-voice stacking, dual saws, strong filter envelope, and a 4-track gated sequence providing acid filter pumping, resonance screaming, and VCA accents over 16 steps at 16th notes. Hold any note to start the sequence. The gated seq envelopes retrigger every step so every 16th note is a discrete punch.",
